A signature Donn Beach drink built on his trademark Pernod-and-bitters secret combination — the same Don's Mix DNA that runs through the Zombie and Cobra's Fang.

In a #shaker{} combine @dark Jamaican rum{1.5%oz}, @light Puerto Rican rum{0.75%oz}, @Cointreau{3%tsp}, @Pernod{0.125%tsp}, @fresh lime juice{0.5%oz}, @falernum{0.5%oz}, and @Angostura bitters{1%dash}.
Add @crushed ice{0.5%cup} and flash blend or shake briefly.
Pour unstrained into a #double old-fashioned glass{}.
Garnish with a @mint sprig{1} and a @maraschino cherry{1}.
